The answers that our situational mana taps give us enough mana, just pretty much sums up their understanding.  Make those independent of a mob having mana like the SK's mana recourse spells and I would agree.  But when our meana regen is dependent upon the mob having mana, then we are SOL.  Fight anywhre in Toer 1 PoP, most places in Plane of Storms, 99% of Valor, etc....and you have nothing to tap.
<br />

<br />
But we all know this right?  Why don't the spell guys get it?
<br />

<br />
Have these spells (ToT and SP) give us recourse without the mob needing to have mana and I'll agree that we don't NEED a self only spell like AotZ.  But without it, the argument that they are good enough has no credibilty.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><img src="images/smiles/icon_pistoles.gif" alt="icon_pistoles.gif" border="0" />  Moderator of The Runes - <span style="font-weight: bold">AKA Griefer Police</span>!
